556
00:49:01,099 --> 00:49:03,280
The pillow. The red pillow.

557
00:49:08,540 --> 00:49:13,019
Thank you. Please do me a favor and release it for me.

558
00:49:13,019 --> 00:49:15,180
My friends are afraid of it.

559
00:49:18,560 --> 00:49:20,819
