597
00:52:28,200 --> 00:52:31,960
No, thanks. I don't want to be your friend.

598
00:52:34,760 --> 00:52:36,293
Then...

599
00:52:38,240 --> 00:52:40,310
I'll let you decide on your own.

600
00:52:40,310 --> 00:52:44,760
Let's say, I am clear with my standing.

601
00:52:44,760 --> 00:52:48,080
Please excuse me. I'll go help others.

602
00:52:50,080 --> 00:52:51,439
